text: Fraser River may refer to: * Fraser River, a river in British Columbia, Canada * Fraser River (Colorado), a tributary of the Colorado River in Colorado in the United States * Fraser River (Newfoundland and Labrador), a river in Labrador, Canada * Fraser River (Western Australia), a river in the Kimberley region of Western Australia * Earnscleugh River, also known as Fraser River, in New Zealand ==See also== *Fraser (disambiguation)
title: Fraser River (disambiguation)
